title: Ep 126 OG Frog: Blood Origins

description:
In this episode of Gangster Chronicles we sit down with OG Frog from the Nickerson Gardens housing projects in Watts, California and discuss the origins of the red rag, touches on King Babalouie, Raymond Washington and much more.
